title: Warau Manekineko
overview: Hitomi Takashiro and Akako Honda are members of comedy duo "Akako to Hitomi." The created the comedy duo about 5 years ago, but they are still not very popular. Every day, they perform Manzai to a regular audience in a corner of a small theater. One day, Hitomi and Akako catch a middle school student trying to steal Hitomi's bicycle. Since then, their fate as a female comedy duo begins to change.
